Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What are these things?}Lũ này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I get that we're in a terrible situation,}Có vẻ tình hình khá tồi tệ,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{and I know that\Nwe're in terrible danger.}và chúng ta đang gặp nguy hiểm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Innocent Zero.}{\i0}Innocent Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I must hurry to assist Mr. Wahlberg.}{\i0}Phải hỗ trợ thầy hiệu trưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So tough.}{\i0}Cứng quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Then...}{\i0}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Each and every one of them\Nhas enough power to be a double-liner.}Mỗi con quỷ đều mạnh tương tương 2 vạch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Orter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Kaldo, head over\Nas backup for Mr. Wahlberg.}Kaldo, mau hỗ trợ thầy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Looks like they don't\Nwant us over there.}Có vẻ chúng không muốn cho ta qua.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Why're there so many?}Sao đông quá vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Quit your whining and get to work!}Đừng cằn nhằn mà lo đánh đi.
